==English==
===Noun===
'''octahedron''' (''plural'' '''octahedra''' ''or'' '''octahedrons''')

#{{geometry}} a [[polyhedron]] with [[eight]] [[face]]s; the [[regular]] octahedron has regular [[triangle]]s as faces and is one of the [[Platonic solid]]s.

